Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Soichiro] What?\N-[man groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this.\NAnother 23 victims yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these confirmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] As soon as we began to suspect\Nthat Kira might be a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the pacing of the killings changed,\Nas if to contradict that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This can only mean that Kira has access\Nto police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] When L discovers that I'm somehow\Ngetting confidential information,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be obligated to start investigating\Nthe police to find the source of the leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being followed by another human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's watching you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to get rid of him\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because through a Shinigami's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a human's name can be seen\Nabove their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that.\NWe see their lifespan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if a Shinigami drops\Nhis Death Note and a human picks it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he can grant that human\Nthe eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for having a Shinigami's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is half of that person's\Nremaining lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what'll it be, Light? Is it a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,PURSUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Ryuk around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was serious\Nabout losing his Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably picked up by some human\Nbefore he could get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Then he'd be stuck there\Ntill the end of that human's life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or until the Death Note is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That could take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't picture\NRyuk doing something so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what? I actually heard\Nhe was carrying two Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shinigami] Seriously?\NWhy would he need two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me. I'll never understand that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] So, the price for receiving\Nthe eyes of a Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is no more than half\Nof my remaining lifespan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, do we have a deal or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This deal is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[dog barking in the distance]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Let's get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan is to create an ideal new world\Nfree from evil and all criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I intend to reign as a god\Nin that world for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I might consider the deal\Nif it lengthened my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but not if I die sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you of all people\Nshould know I wouldn't take this deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I still felt I should tell you\Nthat the deal existed, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've done my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you complaining\NI didn't tell you this earlier on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This is what you call\N"telling me early on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're a little late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why you couldn't have\Ntold me this when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or better yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you could've simply included it\Nin the instructions for the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the slightest bit daunted\Nby the fact that I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't suck up to me, and he seems\Nto have no problem giving me a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Well?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure there's nothing else\Nyou want to tell me "ahead of time,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really? That's too bad.\N-What do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Ryuk, I might've seriously\Nconsidered the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'd offered me wings instead of eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the idea of flying around\Nfreely in the sky sounds very god-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's been mankind's dream\Nsince antiquity to be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd stand out if you sprouted wings\Nand flew around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the police would have\Nno trouble finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if I keep bargaining for eyes\Nand wings and whatever else,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,next thing you know I'm going to end up\Nbecoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though who knows?\NI bet that could be pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without the eyes and the wings,\Nyou're already a worthy Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] The Shinigami Realm\Nis slowly rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We lead meaningless and empty lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only reason\Nwe still take human lives
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we're afraid to die ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of the matter is, we no longer\Neven know why we exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I doubt there's any reason\Nfor our existence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, compared to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're becoming\Na much more impressive Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.\NFrom what you're telling me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds like I'm doing\Na lot more work than they are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be compared\Nto a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a human using this Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the world a better place\Nfor other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] But I wouldn't necessarily say\Nthat the Shinigami realm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is meaningless to humans either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? Why do you say that?\N-Well, just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever a Shinigami like you\Ncomes to the Human World
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,once every hundred, no,\Nmore like every thousand years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the Human World changes dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of the Shinigami Realm\Nis extremely significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You told me just now\Nthat the Shinigami realm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is slowly rotting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you return from this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,why not use what you've learned here\Nto try and change it for the better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Light, I'm not sure\Nwhy I never noticed this until now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're quite the positive thinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs] Yeah, of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using the Death Note\Nto create a better world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be a positive thinker\Nto even attempt something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got what? What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how to find the name of the guy\Nwho was following me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm gonna use the rules\Nof the Death Note to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that if I write down\Na cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got six minutes and forty seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to record the conditions\Nand exact time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I need to know\Nexactly how far I can go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in terms of specifying\Nthe details of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FOLLOWING MORNING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Another six inmates\Nwere found dead last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All were heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bizarre behavior before they died?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So they didn't just die\Nfrom heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what I'm saying\Nis they all died of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but it wasn't quite that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Before one of them died,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he drew a pentagram on the wall\Nof his cell using his own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Another left a letter, but it doesn't seem\Nto be a will or anything meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for the third victim,\Nhe escaped from his cell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran all the way to the staff bathrooms\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more heart attack victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but the circumstances of their deaths\Nare different from what we've seen so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "different"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you a copy of a letter\Nas well as pictures taken at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] It sounds like he was afraid\Nthat Kira would find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's believable that our victim\Nmight have been genuinely afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrote this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but we know Kira can control\Nthe time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he can also determine the actions\Nin the moments leading up to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We can't release details\Nof these men's deaths to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as they're concerned,\Nthese are just heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have reason to believe that Kira\Nwas performing some kind of test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,using these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd only be giving him the results\Nof this information if we go public.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So now he's experimenting on his victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing with people's lives,\Nas if all this was just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If Kira is really using criminals\Nas test subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what is he trying to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The results of yesterday's little "test"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,have already been downloaded\Nonto my dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,KEITO NAWARAMI: KIDNAPPING, MURDER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These results are just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Death Note will work\Nfor what I have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them escaped\Nand ran into the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had specified in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one drew the same symbol I'd\Ndrawn in the Death Note before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,TAMIKI: HEART ATTACK\NESCAPES FROM CELL. DIED 6:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A third wrote the same letter I had\Nwritten in the Death Note. Word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,LORD HAVE MERCY\NI'LL BE HANGED OR KILLED BY KIRA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All three did exactly\Nwhat I intended them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] For the other three inmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I purposely wrote conditions\Nthat were virtually impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,YUZO FURA: DIES IN FRONT OF\NTHE EIFFEL TOWER TODAY AT 6:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With the first one, I wrote that he'd die\Nin front of the Eiffel Tower in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However, everyone knows it's physically\Nimpossible to go from a prison in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to Paris, France in only one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this couldn't happen, he simply died\Nof a heart attack in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The next was supposed to draw\Nan exact picture of L's face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,on the prison wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,KABEOKA: HEART ATTACK\NDRAWS EXACT IMAGE OF L'S FACE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This also didn't happen. You can't draw\Nsomeone you've never seen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINSHIRO YAMAMAE: HEART ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With the last one,\NI tried something slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I specified that he'd write\Na note that read,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I know that L is suspicious\Nof the Japanese police."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI actually expected this one to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it didn't end up happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, it's impossible\Nto make someone write
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what they don't already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be the kind of thing\Nthey could come up with on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, even the Death Note\Ncan't do the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as long as it's within\Nthe realistic limits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of what that person might do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can control them as much as I want\Nbefore they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's all this leading to?\NWhat's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These latest victims will no doubt\Nkeep L and the police guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,he's probably trying to decipher\Nall the clues I left for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially that little note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That absolutely meaningless dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If Kira used those criminals\Nto conduct an experiment of some sort,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it means he's about to start something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he moves now, there's a good chance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the FBI will notice someone\Nacting suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps he has a different goal\Nin mind altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the pentagram and this letter\Nbe some kind of message?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,L, DO YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Time for the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday on the news,\Nthey said this drug addict
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to rob a bank but was unsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,WANTED CRIMINAL\NKIICHIRO OSOREDA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He attacked a few people and then\Nran away empty-handed. I'll use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda last minute,\Nbut I'm sure I can find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I got a few people in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A few people? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see. Believe it or not,\NI'm actually a rather popular guy, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone continues ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh, Light? Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] He's still following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing would just be\Na waste of time if he wasn't tailing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[bus engine chugging]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-A date?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-[giggles]\N-It's a date no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure even my stalker\Nwill see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't just a date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you'd figured out a way\Nto find your stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, tell me, what do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come on. Didn't you see\Nwhat I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I explained it in great detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Doing that would take\Nall the fun out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just be patient\Nand watch what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry, did I keep you waiting?\N-No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I haven't been\Nto Space Land since junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best part is\NI have you all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] During the week, he goes to school\Nand cram school at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dates on his day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal kid. Just a hardworking senior\Nin high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Chief Yagami's son, Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No cause for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[bus door hissing open]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll be done\Nwith my surveillance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that'll be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yuri] I don't get it, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you weren't going out\Nuntil entrance exams were over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was before I scored number one\Non the national practice exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo, you're such a nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yuri giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,EMERGENCY EXIT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[bus approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[door hissing open]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's him! He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven passengers excluding him,\Nno one's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything should go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gun clicking]\N-[driver exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in your seats unless you wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[people exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus-jacking? You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If anybody moves,\NI'm putting a bullet in their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, driver, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've got the number\Nfor Space Land's office on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Call them!\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[driver] This-- This is Sasaki,\Ncalling from bus 174.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them what's going on,\Nand no tricks either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My bus has been hijacked\Nand he's holding a gun to my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Osoreda] Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard what he said. Now you listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a female staff member bring\Nall of Space Land's cash from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's there. Have her meet us\Ntwo bus stops from the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't make me wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you mess with me at all\Nor try to get the police involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll kill\Nevery one of these passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yuri whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yuri, don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as he turns around,\NI'm gonna grab the gun out of his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. That's risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes to that, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We don't have\Nto pass notes back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we keep it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't be able to hear our voices\Nover the sound of the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof\Nthat you're not his accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Accomplice?\N-Yes, I've read about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The first hijacker comes in\Nlike he's working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, a second one\Npretends to be a hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and stays in the very back,\Njust in case something goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You-- You really think he is one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] I've-- I've no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Light Yagami isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was, he could just kill this guy\Nwith a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's proof. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. L needed an outsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so he got the FBI to investigate\Nanyone connected to the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is… Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess for the time being\NI won't bother asking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what an FBI agent is doing on the bus\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you have a gun?\N-[Raye] Yeah, I've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] So if it comes down to it,\NI can rely on you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Raye] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Osoreda] Shut the hell up, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to shoot you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Raye] That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy, his face was all over\Nthe local news just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some junkie who tried to rob a bank
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and ended up killing three people\Nbefore he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] We're safe. He won't shoot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he's not going to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Smart-ass. You guys were planning\Nsomething back here, weren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. If he sees that note from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll find out that Light was planning\Nto jump on him and take his gun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,MINAMI PARK BUS STOP, 11:27\NSPACE LAND BUS STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Osoreda] Plans for a date, huh?\NStupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You in the very back!\NWhat do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been hiding back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You're talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you mean you can actually\Nsee me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims] Stay there, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep away from me, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. He's hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That little note that Light\Naccidentally dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was actually torn from the pages\Nof the Death Note itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he tricked this guy\Ninto touching the paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he's the only other one on the bus\Nwho can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Osoreda yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Shinigami, so I'm afraid\Nyour bullets aren't gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming and gunshots]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Osoreda continues screaming]\N-[gun clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Anyone who touches\Nthe Death Note can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stay till the Death Note\Nis finished or I see you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And a Shinigami can't die from being shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said all these things\Nat one time or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he is the top-ranked student\Nin the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He even used this hijacking\Nas a way to get the guy following him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to willingly give up his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bus! Let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[brakes screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SPACE LAND
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Eleven forty-five on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything went just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] "Kiichiro Osoreda.\NAccidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boards the 11:31 Space Land-bound bus\Nnear the eastern entrance to the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,holding a loaded gun\Nand attempts to hijack the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees a horrific phantom\Nand empties his gun trying to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrified, he flees the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately afterwards, at 11:45,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he dies when struck by a car."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The Death Note never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be next, Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED